SSyynnooppssiiss
       VtSeparator widgetName [options]

DDeessccrriippttiioonn
       Creates  a  Separator  widget  (a  horizontal  or vertical
       line). This is typically used to separate  other  widgets.
       Returns the separator widget's name.

       For  example,  to  create  a separator which goes from the
       left to right side across a  form:  VtSeparator  $form.sep
       -leftSide FORM -rightSide FORM

   OOppttiioonnss
       Sets  the  orientation  to horizontal.  Sets the length of
       the separator (specified in number of characters)  to  int
       in  character  mode.  In graphical mode, set the length of
       the separator to int times the maximum font  width.   Sets
       the orientation to vertical.

